{"tid":1694503,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"修例風波：消息指墮樓科大生腦幹死亡　正準備拔喉","createTime":"2019-11-05T07:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T08:02:53.000Z","uid":130369,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ee174a5f57758d0ebfbfa66ffc73d11de9d115a5","tid":1694503,"uid":130369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:49:29.000Z","msg":"昨日(4日)凌晨於將軍澳屋苑停車場墮樓重傷的周姓科大學生，消息指他已經腦幹死亡，正準備拔喉。據了解，警方仍在調查事主為何當晚會出現在出事停車場。<br />\n根據出事停車場環境，停車場3樓樓層的其中一邊接壤行人路，而另一邊則是高低相差數米的停車場2樓平台，不排除事主當時記錯方向，向2樓平台的一邊逃跑，跨過欄杆，最終墮樓命危。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/news/mobile/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fnews%2Fmobile%2Findex.html&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=f78805ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/news/mobile/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbfb59c94589857ecce5467c6197e1e97f81159","tid":1694503,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:51:15.000Z","msg":"真定假架"},{"pid":"e4676a015f7dd03f9ebe9c77ac79b7881af3c33f","tid":1694503,"uid":130369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cbfb59c94589857ecce5467c6197e1e97f81159","tid":1694503,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:51:15.000Z","msg":"真定假架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:52:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191105/60232901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191105%2F6023